parameters :
    input_refs:
        ui-name : |
            Input Genomes
        short-hint : |
            Genomes for which you want to update the species
    species_names:
        ui-name : |
            New Species names
        short-hint : |
            List of new Species Names (in same order as input Genomes)

description : |
    <p>This method allows the user to add/revise the species names of one or more Genome objects.  If more than one name, the new names must be in the same order as the input Genomes objects and separated by a comma, a newline, or both.</p>
